data.value: In today's digital age, computer laboratories play an important role in facilitating learning and research. Our computer laboratory log management system is an essential attribute that provides for storing logs generated by laboratory computers. This provides a simple and efficient experience. Users can access the laboratory resources by entering their login information, such as their username and password. The logs contain important information about users' usage of the computers, such as the login and logout sessions taken by them. The system ensures that logs are stored efficiently with access controls and encryption to protect against unauthorized admin users. It also includes features for adding new users', searching users' information, filtering logs, and refreshing logs in real-time to carry out an administrative task. This abstract highlights the importance of implementing a log management system to enhance the efficiency of the institution’s computer laboratory.
